n:logicalMetadataWrapperPanel,commentWrapperPanel,galleryWrapperPanel\"\n+                                     oncomplete=\"updateMetadataEditorView(false);\"/>\n+                    <p:commandButton value=\"#{msgs.cancel}\"\n+                                     icon=\"fa fa-times fa-lg\"\n+                                     iconPos=\"secondary\"", "originalCommit": "e6eba2d12e6df403ced3a0e7c983776ff2180031", "replyToReviewId": null, "replies": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQxMjg3Njc0MQ==", "url": "https://github.com/kitodo/kitodo-production/pull/3495#discussion_r412876741", "bodyText": "Funny enough, it seems any value but left results in the icon being displayed on the right side:\n\niconPos=\"left\" -> Icon on the left\niconPos=\"right\" -> Icon on the right\niconPos=\"secondary\" -> Icon on the right\niconPos=\"foobar\" -> Icon on the right\niconPos=\"\" -> Icon on the right\nno iconPos attribute at all -> Icon on the left\n\nSo technically, secondary seems to be valid in order to move the icon to the right, but it's not really intuitive, so I changed it to right like you suggested.", "author": "solth", "createdAt": "2020-04-22T10:49:45Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQxMjg2NDg3Nw=="}], "type": "inlineReview"}, {"oid": "13321a841ab287da25cff8b2c642f115223c8562", "url": "https://github.com/kitodo/kitodo-production/commit/13321a841ab287da25cff8b2c642f115223c8562", "message": "Use correct 'iconPos' value", "committedDate": "2020-04-22T10:51:26Z", "type": "commit"}]}